title: Moapa Valley takes top seed in Division 1A Sunrise with win over Chaparral
text:
Published By: Las Vegas Sun - Today 
Moapa Valley smothered Chaparral 35-6 to claim the Division 1A Sunrise regular-season title Friday night in Overton.
